with a as (
select 
	s.SSEGURO,
	DECODE(CAST(s.cestat AS VARCHAR) , CAST(4 AS VARCHAR), CAST((select p.npoliza from cdp_ods.sisaxis_cmi_propuesta p where CAST(p.sciclo AS VARCHAR) = s.crfaage and p.csistema='1' and p.ctipdoc=1) AS VARCHAR), '') n_poliza,
	CAST((select p.npoliza from cdp_ods.sisaxis_cmi_propuesta p where p.sciclo = cast(decode(s.crfaage,'',null,s.crfaage) as numeric) and p.csistema='1' and p.ctipdoc=1 and p.npoliza is not null) AS VARCHAR) policy_web, --added as part of DID_239
	s.ssolicit,
	s.cramo,
	s.sproduc,
	t.nnumnif rut_cont,
	t.cpertip,
	t.csexper,
	(SELECT P.TAPELLI FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AGENTES  A LEFT JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  P ON A.SPERSON= P.SPERSON  AND A.CTIPAGE=1 WHERE A.CAGENTE = '00000'|| SUBSTRING(s.CAGENTE,LENGTH(s.CAGENTE)-2,3) )A_NOMBRE_SUCURSAL,
	DECODE(t.cpertip, 1, RTRIM(LTRIM(t.tapelli1)) || ' ' || RTRIM(LTRIM(t.tapelli2)) || '- ' || RTRIM(LTRIM(t.tnombre)), NVL(RTRIM(LTRIM(t.tapelli)), RTRIM(LTRIM(t.tnombre)))) contratante,
	a.nnumnif rut_asegurado,
	DECODE(a.cpertip, 1, RTRIM (LTRIM (a.tapell1)) || ' ' || RTRIM (LTRIM (a.tapell2)) || '- ' || RTRIM (LTRIM (a.tnombre)), RTRIM (LTRIM (a.tnombre)) || ' ' || RTRIM (LTRIM (a.tapell1)) || RTRIM (LTRIM (a.tapell2))) asegurado,
	s.falta,
	cagente,
	TO_NUMBER(SUBSTRING(s.CAGENTE,LENGTH(s.CAGENTE)-2,3),'999') A_ID_SUCURSAL,
	s.cusuari,
	s.fanula,
	crfaage,
	s.cestat,
	s.fefecto,
	s.fvencim,
	s.fcaranu,
	s.facepta,
	s.CACTIVI,
	s.cagrseg,
	null as ctipseg,
	null as cmodali,
	null as ccolect,
	null as cmarca,
	null as smodelo,
	null as nanofab,
        cast(0 as INT) as emission1,
	cast(0 as INT) as robot,
	cast(0 as INT) as tipo_corredor,
	cast('axis' as varchar(12)) as src_sys_cd,  
	cast(0 as INT) as tipo_nego,
	cast(0 as INT) as tipo_emission, 
	cast('web' as VARCHAR(8)) as quote_source

from cdp_ods.sisaxis_solseguros s, cdp_ods.sisaxis_solidproductos i, cdp_ods.sisaxis_soltomadores t, cdp_ods.sisaxis_solasegurados a
where s.cramo<>6 
and t.ssolicit=s.ssolicit
and a.ssolicit=s.ssolicit
and s.ssolicit=i.ssolicit(+)
and s.falta BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/01/2018', 'dd/MM/yyyy HH24:MI:SS')  AND getdate()),

c as (
SELECT T1.SSOLICIT AS C_SSOLICIT, 
nvl(MAX(PDTOCOM)/100,0) C_PDTOCOM
FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLGARANSEG T1 INNER JOIN (SELECT SSOLICIT FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLSEGUROS WHERE 
FALTA BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/01/2018', 'dd/MM/yyyy HH24:MI:SS')  AND getdate() ) T2 
ON T1.SSOLICIT = T2.SSOLICIT
GROUP BY T1.SSOLICIT),

d as (
SELECT T1.SSOLICIT AS D_SSOLICIT,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =1 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_00,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =2 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_03,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =3 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_05,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =4 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_10
FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLPREGUNSEGPROP T1 INNER JOIN  (SELECT SSOLICIT FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLSEGUROS WHERE 
FALTA BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/01/2018', 'dd/MM/yyyy HH24:MI:SS') AND getdate() ) T2 
ON T1.SSOLICIT = T2.SSOLICIT
WHERE CPREGUN =1000
GROUP BY T1.SSOLICIT ),

f as (
SELECT   A.CAGENTE AS F_CAGENTE,   
         SubString(P.NNUMNIF,1,Length(P.NNUMNIF)-1) +  SubString(P.NNUMNIF,Length(P.NNUMNIF),1)  F_RUT_CORREDOR,
         REPLACE(TBUSCAR,'#','') F_NOMBRE_CORREDOR
FROM CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_AGENTES A INNER JOIN CDP_ODS.SISAXIS_PERSONAS P ON A.SPERSON = P.SPERSON ),
g as (
SELECT CAST(CAST(sciclo AS NUMERIC(38,0)) AS VARCHAR) AS sciclo, count(1) as sciclo_count
from cdp_ods.sisaxis_cmi_propuesta  where csistema=1 and ctipdoc=1 and npoliza is not null and npoliza > 0 group by sciclo -- and npoliza > 0
)


select h.*, lob.dim_lob_key, ins.mdik, bro.dim_broker_key, suc.dim_branch_office_key,
null as B_SSEGURO_1,
null as B_NPOLIZA_1,
null as B_NCERTIF_1,
null as B_SPRODUC_1,
null as B_IPIRIANUSEG_1,
null as B_IPRITAR_1,
null as B_PDTOCOM_1,
null as B_IFRAQUSEG_1,
null as B_FEMISIO_1,
null as B_FEFECTO_1,
null as B_FIN_VIG_1,
null as B_FVENCIM_1,
null as B_CACTIVI_1,
null as B_FANULAC_1,
null as B_TTITULO_1,
null as B_CAGENTE_1,
null as B_ID_SUCURSAL_1,
null as B_NOMBRE_SUCURSAL_1,
null as B_TBUSCAR_1,
null as B_NNUMNIF_1,
null as B_SPERSON_1,
null as B_CMARCA_1,
null as B_SMODELO_1,
null as B_NANOFAB_1,
null as B_CSITUAC_1,
null as E_NOMBRE_USUARIO,
null as E_CUSUARI, 
null as E_CPERFIL,
null as E_DESC_PERFIL_USUARIO,
null as E_DESCUENTO_PERMITIDO,
case when (sciclo_count>0)   then 1 else 0 end as emission_web,
case when (emission1=1 or emission_web=1) then 1 else 0 end as emission_or_web

from (
select acdfg.*, max_sid from
(select acdf.*, g.*   from 
(select acd.*, f.* from 
(select ac.*,d.* from
(select a.*,c.* from a 
left join c
on a.SSOLICIT = c.C_SSOLICIT) ac
left join d on
ac.SSOLICIT = d.D_SSOLICIT) acd
left join f 
on acd.CAGENTE = f.F_CAGENTE) acdf
left join g on
acdf.CRFAAGE = g.sciclo) acdfg
left join 
(select 1 dummy, max(fact_quote_key) max_sid from cdp_dwh.fact_quotation_t_test) LKP_MAX_KEY
on LKP_MAX_KEY.dummy=1 ) h
left join (select * from cdp_dwh.dim_lob_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis') lob
on h.cramo = lob.lob_cd AND h.cusuari <> 'FPAXIS2' and h.cusuari <> 'ANIDA1'
left join (select insured_rut_num, max(dim_insured_key) as mdik  from cdp_dwh.dim_insured_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis' group by insured_rut_num) ins
on h.rut_asegurado = SUBSTRING(ins.insured_rut_num,1,LENGTH(ins.insured_rut_num)-1)
left join (select * from cdp_dwh.dim_broker_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis') bro
on h.f_rut_corredor = bro.broker_id
left join (select * from cdp_dwh.dim_branch_office_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis') suc
on h.a_id_sucursal = suc.branch_office_id;
